### Product
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/products
X-API-Key: dev-api-key
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "productId": "P100",
  "code": "SENSOR-100",
  "name": "Industrial Sensor"
}

### Revision A
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/revisions
X-API-Key: dev-api-key
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "revisionId": "P100-REV-A",
  "productId": "P100",
  "code": "A",
  "status": "APPROVED"
}

